value.0: A rather sickly and emaciated kobold walks towards you, sniffing the air. "Grr. You comes bringing gifts? You brings honey for us, yip?"
"Me no smells honey on you. Yip!, you goes and gets honey, or we no feeds you. That be agreement, yip!"
"Yip! That be agreement! You breaks agreement, you dies, grrr!"
"Yip, yip! You goes and gets honey! We no feeds you 'til then! Yip!"
"Yip! With the master be our agreement, of course, yip!"
"Yip! You not knows master? You be intruder, maybe? Grr, me not care, if you gives us honey! You get honey!"
"Honey set kobold minds free, yip! Kobolds gains big thoughts with honey help! There be nothing likes honey, yip!"
"Me smells honey on you, yip! You gives to us, then we feeds you, just like agreed yip!"
